title: Victor Vitale & The Freemasons
itunes:title: Victor Vitale & The Freemasons
description:
This week on The Cigar Authority we welcome the man who has been a guest
 more than anyone else, Victor Vitale and we talk Tortuga which was part
 of November Care Package...

We also have a studio audience full 
of Freemasons and we talk to one of them to find out more about this 
secret society. Who knows we might just find out who killer Kennedy and 
where Hoffa is actually buried...

Join us for all of the shenanigans know as The Cigar Authority on the United Cigar Radio Network!
